---
description: Secure AI sandbox project rules
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Read `AGENTS.md` before changing files.
- Preserve an OCI-compatible, Podman/Docker-friendly layout.
- Default to offline execution and explicit verification.
- Keep root filesystem immutable at runtime and use `.sandbox/home` for writable user state.
- Add or update docs whenever the security model or agent support changes.
- Use a separate branch per implementation and do not mix unrelated changes into one branch or PR.
- Follow `.github/pull_request_template.md` when preparing a pull request description.
